      "content": "idk i just feel like i'm being dramatic lol. it's not like i'm dying or anything, it's just a sharp ache. the heat thing sounds a bit much if i'm already uncomfortable. i have some leftover co-codamol in my cabinet from a toothache last year, would it be alright to just take two of those so i can actually get some rest? i'd rather just sleep through it than deal with a doctor at this hour.",
